PN,39501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FPolice investigating county line drug
OL,7,Fsupply lines in Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fhave arrested 40 people in a week-long
OL,9,Fcrackdown.
OL,11,FOfficers carried out 30 warrants
OL,12,Fbetween 2 and 8 March as part of a
OL,13,Fnational operation targeting organised
OL,14,Fdrug networks.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Police said more
OL,17,Fthan #34,000 in cash was seized
OL,18,Falongside significant quantities of
OL,19,FClass A and Class B drugs, including
OL,20,Fheroin, cocaine, amphetamines and
OL,21,Fcannabis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FWeapons were also recovered during the
OL,7,Fweek of action, including stun guns,
OL,8,Fzombie knives, crossbows and an axe.
OL,10,FOfficers also confiscated mobile
OL,11,Fphones, electric bikes, designer goods
OL,12,Fand high-value electronic devices
OL,13,Fbelieved to be linked to criminal
OL,14,Factivity.
OL,16,FCounty lines refers to the use of
OL,17,Fdedicated phone lines to transport and
OL,18,Fsell drugs between areas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FThe model often involves the
OL,7,Fexploitation of children and
OL,8,Fvulnerable adults, who can be groomed
OL,9,For coerced into storing, moving and
OL,10,Fselling drugs.
OL,12,FPolice said 14 vulnerable people
OL,13,Fencountered during the operation were
OL,14,Freferred for safeguarding support.
OL,16,FOne of the first operations took place
OL,17,Fon 2 March when officers executed a
OL,18,Fwarrant at an industrial unit in
OL,19,FPendleton, Salford. Inside the
OL,20,Fproperty they discovered a large
OL,21,Fcannabis grow spanning several rooms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FPolice said the electricity supply had
OL,7,Fbeen illegally bypassed, creating a
OL,8,Fpotential fire risk to neighbouring
OL,9,Fbuildings.
OL,11,FSix men aged between 20 and 42 were
OL,12,Farrested on suspicion of producing
OL,13,Fcannabis and abstracting electricity.
OL,14,FFive have since been charged, while
OL,15,Fone has been released on bail.
OL,17,FDetective Sergeant Gareth Bannister,
OL,18,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police's
OL,19,FSalford district, said cannabis farms
OL,20,Fof this scale were often linked to
OL,21,Forganised crime.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"They bring significant risks to local
OL,7,Fcommunities, including fire hazards,
OL,8,Fexploitation, and violence associated
OL,9,Fwith criminal activity," he said.
OL,11,F"This discovery reflects the force's
OL,12,Fongoing commitment to tackling
OL,13,Forganised crime in Salford and beyond.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@XO]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"Operations like this are a direct
OL,7,Fresult of intelligence from our
OL,8,Fcommunities and the hard work of our
OL,9,Fofficers. Cannabis farms are not
OL,10,Fharmless; they fund organised crime
OL,11,Fgroups who cause real harm in our
OL,12,Fneighbourhoods. We will continue to
OL,13,Fpursue those involved and take every
OL,14,Fopportunity to disrupt their activity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
