OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FDuring the week, officers from
OL,7,FOldham's Challenger team carried out
OL,8,Ftwo early morning warrants at a
OL,9,Fresidential address and a business
OL,10,Fpremises as part of an investigation
OL,11,Finto a drug supply line operating in
OL,12,Fthe area.
OL,14,FPolice said a suspect attempted to
OL,15,Fflee from the back of one property but
OL,16,Fwas detained by officers surrounding
OL,17,Fthe address.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FA man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,7,Fconspiracy to supply Class A drugs and
OL,8,Fofficers seized drugs and a mobile
OL,9,Fphone.
OL,11,FFurther warrants carried out as part
OL,12,Fof the investigation led to additional
OL,13,Farrests, with five men charged.
OL,15,FOn 6 March, three further warrants
OL,16,Fwere executed across Northenden and
OL,17,FSalford in connection with a county
OL,18,Flines operation linked to the supply
OL,19,Fof drugs including ketamine, cocaine
OL,20,Fand cannabis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FThree men and one woman were arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of drug offences.
OL,9,FPolice said officers recovered
OL,10,Fquantities of drugs as well as cash
OL,11,Fand mobile phones. Four people have
OL,12,Fbeen charged.
OL,14,FAlongside enforcement activity, police
OL,15,Fand partner organisations carried out
OL,16,Fpreventative work with young people.
OL,17,FOfficers delivered talks at Mount
OL,18,FSaint Joseph's High School in Bolton
OL,19,Fto raise awareness of how county lines
OL,20,Fnetworks operate and how young people
OL,21,Fcan be targeted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FPolice said the sessions were designed
OL,7,Fto help pupils recognise warning signs
OL,8,Fof exploitation and understand how to
OL,9,Freport concerns.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector John Schofield,
OL,12,Ffrom Greater Manchester Police's
OL,13,FSerious and Organised Crime Unit, said
OL,14,Finformation from local communities had
OL,15,Fplayed a key role in the operation.
OL,17,F"We have had a very busy and
OL,18,Fsuccessful County Lines
OL,19,FIntensification Week, with various
OL,20,Flines disrupted thanks to the warrants
OL,21,Fwe have executed," he said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"Intelligence gathered from the
OL,7,Fcommunity played a vital role in us
OL,8,Fbeing able to conduct this activity,
OL,9,Fwhich saw 30 warrants resulting in 40
OL,10,Farrests and 20 drug lines closed down
OL,11,Facross Greater Manchester. This week's
OL,12,Faction is a powerful example of our
OL,13,Fcommitment to dismantle organised
OL,14,Fcrime in our region.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"Working with partners meant we were
OL,7,Falso able to deliver a comprehensive
OL,8,Fprevent programme so we could engage
OL,9,Fwith young people in Greater
OL,10,FManchester. Drugs gangs that target
OL,11,Fand exploit children are child
OL,12,Fabusers, and we are increasingly
OL,13,Flooking to prosecute offenders through
OL,14,Fthe Modern Slavery Act. Young people
OL,15,Fbeing exploited by drugs gangs are not
OL,16,Fcriminals, and we are here to work
OL,17,Fwith partners to protect them and
OL,18,Fprevent further harm."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,FThe Deputy Mayor for Safer and
OL,7,FStronger Communities, Kate Green, said
OL,8,Fcounty lines activity continues to
OL,9,Fcause significant harm to communities.
OL,11,F"County lines activity brings
OL,12,Fsignificant harm to our communities.
OL,13,FIt fuels the supply of dangerous drugs
OL,14,Fwhile exploiting children and
OL,15,Fvulnerable adults who are often
OL,16,Fgroomed, coerced and threatened into
OL,17,Fcriminal activity," she said.
OL,19,F"That is why tackling this type of
OL,20,Forganised crime is a key priority for
OL,21,Fpartners across Greater Manchester.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@SO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"Through Programme Challenger, we are
OL,7,Fbringing together policing, local
OL,8,Fauthorities, schools and safeguarding
OL,9,Fservices to pursue those responsible,
OL,10,Fclose down drug lines and protect the
OL,11,Fyoung people and vulnerable adults who
OL,12,Fare being exploited.
OL,14,F"The activity during this week of
OL,15,Faction shows what can be achieved when
OL,16,Fpartners work together with
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773436324
OL,3,CPolice arrest 40 people in week-long
OL,4,Ccrackdown on county lines
OL,6,F"We will continue to take robust
OL,7,Faction against those responsible for
OL,8,Fcounty lines activity while making
OL,9,Fsure people at risk of exploitation
OL,10,Fget the support and protection they
OL,11,Fneed."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
